Apply Straying

apply_straying.Rd

Function to apply adult upstream straying

apply_straying(
  year,
  natural_adults,
  hatchery_adults,
  total_releases,
  release_month,
  flows_oct_nov,
  flows_apr_may,
  monthly_mean_pdo
)

Arguments

year

Simulation year

natural_adults

Number of natural adults

hatchery_adults

Number of hatchery adults

total_releases

Total hatchery fish released from..params$hatchery_release,

release_month

Hatchery release month, defaults to 1,

flows_oct_nov

Mean flows from October and November from ..params$flows_oct_nov,

flows_apr_may

Mean flows from April and May ..params$flows_apr_may,

monthly_mean_pdo

Mean pdo from winterRunDSM::monthly_mean_pdo,
